# Logos
Official RelevantTec logo assets. Do not modify, distort, or recolor.

## Variants

### Bars (horizontal lockup)
- **bar_dark** — light logo for dark backgrounds
- **bar_white** — dark logo for light backgrounds
- **bar_white_large** — high-res version
- **bar_white_md** — medium-res version
- **bar_grey** — grey variant

### Icons (square mark)
- **ico_black** — black icon
- **ico_grey** — grey icon
- **ico_white** — white icon
- **chat_ico_white** — chat/messaging variant

### Backgrounds
- **background** — standard background
- **background_dark** — dark theme background
- **background_mission** — mission statement background

### Other
- **logo_2line** — stacked two-line logo
